<section id="research" class="mb-16">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-4">1. Initial Research & Shortlisting</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">The first step is knowing where to look and what criteria to use for initial screening. A structured approach saves weeks of wasted communication with unsuitable suppliers. Start your supplier search with these channels:</p>
 <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-600 mb-4">
 <li><strong>B2B platforms</strong>, Alibaba, Global Sources, Made-in-China for initial vetting</li>
 <li><strong>Trade shows</strong>, Canton Fair (Guangzhou), CES (Las Vegas), electronica (Munich)</li>
 <li><strong>Industry referrals</strong>, Ask your network for supplier recommendations</li>
 <li><strong>Direct outreach</strong>, Contact Shenzhen factories directly via their websites</li>
 </ul>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Look for suppliers with at least 5+ years in business, verified factory audits (BV/SGS/TUV), and clear OEM/ODM case studies on their website. A professional B2B supplier website with detailed product specs, certification information, and company history is a strong sign of a legitimate manufacturer. It's much less likely to be a trading company. <a href="/products/power-bank" class="text-brandBlue font-bold hover:text-brandOrange transition">Browse our OEM/ODM power bank lineup →</a></p>
 </section>

 <section id="verify" class="mb-16">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-4">2. How to Verify a China Charger Factory?</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Before committing to any supplier, conduct thorough verification. A legitimate manufacturer should welcome your questions and provide documentation without hesitation. Use this checklist to evaluate potential partners systematically:</p>
 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
 <div class="p-6 bg-green-50 rounded-2xl border border-green-200">
 <h3 class="font-black text-green-700 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Green Flags</h3>
 <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
 <li>ISO 9001 certified production facility</li>
 <li>On-site QC team with documented processes</li>
 <li>Client references from reputable brands</li>
 <li>Transparent factory tour (in-person or video)</li>
 <li>CE/FCC/UL test reports available</li>
 <li>In-house R&D engineering team</li>
 </ul>
 </div>
 <div class="p-6 bg-red-50 rounded-2xl border border-red-200">
 <h3 class="font-black text-red-700 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Red Flags</h3>
 <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
 <li>No verifiable factory address</li>
 <li>Refuses video call factory tour</li>
 <li>Cannot provide test reports</li>
 <li>Extremely low pricing vs market</li>
 <li>Unwilling to sign NDA or contract</li>
 <li>Push for full payment upfront</li>
 </ul>
 </div>
 </div>
