 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-4">3. Understanding OEM vs ODM Terms</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Before negotiating, understand which manufacturing model fits your needs. Your choice between OEM and ODM affects pricing, lead time, and product control. Many successful brands start with ODM to test the market. Then they transition to custom OEM once they have proven demand and volume.</p>
