 <tr class="border-b border-slate-100"><td class="p-4 font-bold">Tooling Cost</td><td class="p-4">$5,000-$30,000</td><td class="p-4">$0 (existing molds)</td></tr>
 <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 bg-slate-50"><td class="p-4 font-bold">Lead Time</td><td class="p-4">45-60 days</td><td class="p-4">25-30 days</td></tr>
