 <section id="red-flags" class="mb-16 p-8 bg-red-50 rounded-3xl border border-red-200">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-red-700 uppercase italic mb-4">6. Red Flags to Watch For</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Experienced buyers know that spotting warning signs early separates successful sourcing relationships from costly failures. Here are the most important red flags to watch for when evaluating a potential China charger supplier:</p>
 <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
 <li><svg class="icon-circle-exclamation text-red-500 mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
 <path d="M256 512a256 256 0 1 1 0-512 256 256 0 1 1 0 512zm0-192a32 32 0 1 0 0 64 32 32 0 1 0 0-64zm0-192c-18.2 0-32.7 15.5-31.4 33.7l7.4 104c.9 12.6 11.4 22.3 23.9 22.3 12.6 0 23-9.7 23.9-22.3l7.4-104c1.3-18.2-13.1-33.7-31.4-33.7z" fill="currentColor"/>
 </svg> <strong>No physical address</strong>, If they only provide a PO box or residential address, walk away. <a href="https://www.google.com/maps" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brandBlue hover:underline">Google Maps</a> can help you verify factory locations before engaging seriously.</li>
 <li><svg class="icon-circle-exclamation text-red-500 mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
 <path d="M256 512a256 256 0 1 1 0-512 256 256 0 1 1 0 512zm0-192a32 32 0 1 0 0 64 32 32 0 1 0 0-64zm0-192c-18.2 0-32.7 15.5-31.4 33.7l7.4 104c.9 12.6 11.4 22.3 23.9 22.3 12.6 0 23-9.7 23.9-22.3l7.4-104c1.3-18.2-13.1-33.7-31.4-33.7z" fill="currentColor"/>
 </svg> <strong>Too many product categories</strong>, A factory claiming to make everything (phones, chargers, toys) is likely a trading company, not a manufacturer</li>
 <li><svg class="icon-circle-exclamation text-red-500 mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
 <path d="M256 512a256 256 0 1 1 0-512 256 256 0 1 1 0 512zm0-192a32 32 0 1 0 0 64 32 32 0 1 0 0-64zm0-192c-18.2 0-32.7 15.5-31.4 33.7l7.4 104c.9 12.6 11.4 22.3 23.9 22.3 12.6 0 23-9.7 23.9-22.3l7.4-104c1.3-18.2-13.1-33.7-31.4-33.7z" fill="currentColor"/>
 </svg> <strong>Stock photos</strong>, Reverse image search their product photos. If they appear on multiple supplier sites, they're not the real manufacturer</li>
 <li><svg class="icon-circle-exclamation text-red-500 mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
 <path d="M256 512a256 256 0 1 1 0-512 256 256 0 1 1 0 512zm0-192a32 32 0 1 0 0 64 32 32 0 1 0 0-64zm0-192c-18.2 0-32.7 15.5-31.4 33.7l7.4 104c.9 12.6 11.4 22.3 23.9 22.3 12.6 0 23-9.7 23.9-22.3l7.4-104c1.3-18.2-13.1-33.7-31.4-33.7z" fill="currentColor"/>
 </svg> <strong>Pressure for immediate payment</strong>, A reliable supplier gives you time to evaluate samples and negotiate proper terms without pressure tactics</li>
 <li><svg class="icon-circle-exclamation text-red-500 mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
 <path d="M256 512a256 256 0 1 1 0-512 256 256 0 1 1 0 512zm0-192a32 32 0 1 0 0 64 32 32 0 1 0 0-64zm0-192c-18.2 0-32.7 15.5-31.4 33.7l7.4 104c.9 12.6 11.4 22.3 23.9 22.3 12.6 0 23-9.7 23.9-22.3l7.4-104c1.3-18.2-13.1-33.7-31.4-33.7z" fill="currentColor"/>
 </svg> <strong>No English documentation</strong>, Professional B2B suppliers provide clear English contracts, PI, and QC documents. Avoid suppliers who only communicate in Chinese if you are not fluent.</li>
 </ul>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">A trustworthy manufacturer like WOWOHCOOL welcomes due diligence. We provide factory tour videos, client references, and verifiable certification numbers. If a supplier hesitates to share this information, consider it a significant warning sign and move to the next candidate on your shortlist.</p>
 </section>

 <!-- Communication & Sample Ordering -->
 <section id="communication" class="mb-16">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-4">7. Communication &amp; Sample Ordering Process</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Effective communication with Chinese suppliers is a learned skill that directly impacts your sourcing success. Clear, detailed communication prevents costly misunderstandings about specs, pricing, and delivery timelines. Here's how to navigate the process from first email to sample approval:</p>

 <div class="bg-brandBlue/5 border-l-4 border-brandOrange p-5 rounded-r-xl mb-8">
 <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm"><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Most Chinese suppliers use WeChat for business communication, it's faster than email and allows photo/video sharing during production. At WOWOHCOOL, we assign a dedicated English-speaking project manager who responds within 4 hours during business days.</p>
 </div>

 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6">
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-4 text-sm"><svg class="icon-comments text-brandOrange mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 576 512">
 <path d="M384 144c0 97.2-86 176-192 176-26.7 0-52.1-5-75.2-14L35.2 349.2c-9.3 4.9-20.7 3.2-28.2-4.2s-9.2-18.9-4.2-28.2l35.6-67.2C14.3 220.2 0 183.6 0 144 0 46.8 86-32 192-32S384 46.8 384 144zm0 368c-94.1 0-172.4-62.1-188.8-144 120-1.5 224.3-86.9 235.8-202.7 83.3 19.2 145 88.3 145 170.7 0 39.6-14.3 76.2-38.4 105.6l35.6 67.2c4.9 9.3 3.2 20.7-4.2 28.2s-18.9 9.2-28.2 4.2L459.2 498c-23.1 9-48.5 14-75.2 14z" fill="currentColor"/>
 </svg>Effective Communication Tips</h3>
 <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-sm">
 <li><strong>Be specific with specs</strong>, Send a detailed RFQ with PDF spec sheet, target price, and required certifications. Vague inquiries get vague responses.</li>
 <li><strong>Respect time zones</strong>, China Standard Time (UTC+8). Send messages before 10am CST for same-day replies. Avoid contacting during Chinese New Year (typically 2-3 week factory shutdown).</li>
 <li><strong>Use simple English</strong>, Short sentences, bullet points, and numbered lists work better than complex paragraphs. Avoid idioms and slang.</li>
 <li><strong>Request photos/video</strong>, Ask for real-time photos of materials, production progress, and packaging. Legitimate suppliers will gladly share.</li>
 </ul>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6">
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-4 text-sm"><svg class="icon-box text-brandOrange mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
 <path d="M369.4 128l-34.3-48-222.1 0-34.3 48 290.7 0zM0 148.5c0-13.3 4.2-26.3 11.9-37.2L60.9 42.8C72.9 26 92.3 16 112.9 16l222.1 0c20.7 0 40.1 10 52.1 26.8l48.9 68.5c7.8 10.9 11.9 23.9 11.9 37.2L448 416c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64L64 480c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64L0 148.5z" fill="currentColor"/>
 </svg>Sample Ordering Workflow</h3>
 <ol class="space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-sm">
 <li><strong>1. RFQ &amp; Spec Confirmation</strong>, Provide detailed product specifications. Supplier confirms feasibility and quotes sample cost.</li>
 <li><strong>2. Sample Fee Payment</strong>, Typical sample fee: $30-150 for ODM models, $200-800 for custom OEM samples. Most suppliers refund sample fees with bulk orders.</li>
 <li><strong>3. Production</strong>, -7 days for standard ODM samples, 15-25 days for custom OEM tooling and samples.</li>
 <li><strong>4. Sample Shipping</strong>, DHL/FedEx/UPS, 3-5 days delivery. Sample shipping cost typically $50-100.</li>
 <li><strong>5. Testing &amp; Approval</strong>, Inspect physical build, test charging performance, verify certifications. Sign off or request revisions. Most brands require 2-3 sample iterations before final approval.</li>
 </ol>
 </div>
 </div>

