 <div class="bg-brandBlue/5 border-l-4 border-brandOrange p-5 rounded-r-xl">
 <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm"><strong>Planning Ahead:</strong> Add 2-4 weeks buffer for custom OEM projects with new tooling, certification delays, or holiday periods (Chinese New Year in Jan/Feb, National Week in Oct). WOWOHCOOL provides a detailed production schedule with weekly progress updates for all OEM/ODM orders.</p>
 </div>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-6">If your product requires UL, CE, or FCC certifications, add 4-8 weeks for initial testing. Working with a manufacturer that has pre-certified product platforms can significantly reduce this timeline since testing focuses on variations rather than entirely new certifications. WOWOHCOOL's pre-certified charger platforms help brands reach market 6-10 weeks faster than developing products from scratch with an uncertified factory.</p>
 </section>

