 <section id="faq" class="mb-16 p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
 <div class="space-y-6">
 <div>
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandOrange text-sm mb-2">How do I find a reliable charger supplier in China?</h3>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Start with verified B2B platforms (Alibaba Gold Supplier, Global Sources), check for ISO 9001 certification, request factory video tours, and always order samples before bulk purchases.</p>
 </div>
 <div>
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandOrange text-sm mb-2">What is the standard MOQ for Chinese charger factories?</h3>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">MOQ varies by product type. Standard ODM models start at 500 units (WOWOHCOOL, Allway), while OEM custom projects typically require 1,000-3,000 units due to tooling costs.</p>
 </div>
 <div>
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandOrange text-sm mb-2">How can I verify a China factory is legitimate?</h3>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Request a video call factory tour, check their business license, verify ISO certifications, search for reviews on sourcing forums, and consider third-party audit services like SGS or BV.</p>
 </div>
 <div>
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandOrange text-sm mb-2">What's the difference between a factory and a trading company?</h3>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">A factory owns production lines and can show you their manufacturing process. A trading company sources from multiple factories and adds a margin. Trading companies aren't always bad, but you'll get better pricing and QC control directly from the manufacturer.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </section>

 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Choosing the right China charger supplier is one of the most important decisions for your product brand. Time invested in proper factory verification, sample testing, and transparent communication pays dividends in product quality and reliable delivery. WOWOHCOOL has been helping global brands navigate China sourcing since 2013 with ISO 9001 certified production and complete OEM/ODM support.</p>

